data.description: This is a golden opportunity you won't want to let slip by. Situated in close proximity to Fort Carson and to Fountain Mesa. This lovely bi-level home offers both convenience and charm. It's conveniently located within walking distance of various shopping centers, making daily errands a breeze.    The upper level of this home is a true gem, featuring three spacious bedrooms and two bathrooms. The entire upper level has beautiful hardwood flooring. What sets this property apart is the enclosed patio that seamlessly transitions to an inviting exterior deck. It's the ideal spot to savor your evenings in complete privacy, surrounded by the tranquility of mature trees.    This home has an impressive basement that can serve multiple purposes. It has two additional bedrooms and a well-maintained bathroom, providing extra living space for your family or guests. The basement even has its own separate entrance, ensuring both security and privacy. A wood-burning fireplace adds warmth and coziness to the space, and there's another full kitchen, making it perfect for generating rental income. This feature presents a fantastic opportunity to offset your mortgage expenses.    In essence, this property is a rare find with a multitude of possibilities. It's patiently waiting for the perfect new owners to appreciate its unique attributes and the potential for financial gain. Don't let this opportunity pass you by; seize it today!
